WEBVTT

00:00.476 --> 00:03.045
Previously on AMC's "The Son"...

00:03.047 --> 00:04.713
Eli: You rode through an oil seep.

00:04.715 --> 00:06.750
Man: It's on Pedro García's land.

00:06.753 --> 00:07.916
What do we do about Pete?

00:07.918 --> 00:09.101
Keep him in the dark.

00:09.104 --> 00:11.653
Maria García was still
a member of that family.

00:11.655 --> 00:13.188
What happened with Sally?

00:13.190 --> 00:14.856
Man #2: She's gonna stay in the city.

00:14.858 --> 00:16.625
Your Honor, there are a few records

00:16.627 --> 00:18.060
we would like to have altered.

00:18.062 --> 00:19.895
Woman: You and your men killed everyone,

00:19.897 --> 00:20.996
except my father.

00:20.998 --> 00:22.631
That was a long time ago.

00:23.552 --> 00:25.801
- Who did this?!
- I didn't see the fella.

00:25.803 --> 00:27.936
Damn, look at 'em all.

00:27.938 --> 00:29.605
